title: [FSX/P3D] FTX Orbx W28 Sequim Valley
description:
W28 Sequim Valley ....... HAPPY FLYING

Welcome to Sunny Sequim! Sequim Valley is a small airfield on the northern Olympic Peninsula and is considered to be a pilot's dream. In the foothills of the spectacular Olympic Mountains, the 3,500ft runway will lead you to some of the most spectacular locations in the Pacific Northwest. The airport is packed with points of interest, fully custom models and only a stones throw away from the hustle and bustle of Seattle and Vancouver. The first release by Jordan Gough, experience the wonders of the Olympic Peninsula from the luxury of your home!

    Crisp 30cm and 60cm per pixel ground imagery
    Detailed modelling with advanced shadowing techniques
    Superb 1m per pixel imagery for the Olympic Mountains
    5 seasonal variations including Hard Winter
    Only 85km from Seattle and 130km from Downtown Vancouver
    PLEASE NOTE: 2WA1 Diamond Point is required for the Dungeness Spit to be Photoreal!
    Blends seamlessly with FTX Pacific Northwest
    Debut release by Jordan Gough
